author: rahul
msg: Improve dialog-config.xml parsing for SCXML dialogs. Introduce the notion of DialogMetadata, a POJO that contains all the relevant bits that Commons SCXML needs to create an instance of a particular dialog.

DialogMetadata is used to account for the bits of Shale dialogs specific XML vocabulary, which obviously special cases from a generic state machine vocabulary -- for example, the attribute for the dialog data class name.
